  "title": "Semi-arid tropical rainfed agriculture: opportunities and challenges",
  "abstract": "This paper reviews the achievements of ICRISAT's research in dry farming insemi-arid tropical regions with special reference to its five mandate crops, sorghum, pearl millet, pigeonpea, chickpea and groundnut. A brief discussion on ICRISAT's future plans is included",
